To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private RelativeVigorIndex _rvi;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_rvi = RVI(symbol, period);

// In OnData()
if (_rvi.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "signal", _rvi.Signal.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "relativevigorindex", _rvi.Current.Value);
}
# In Initialize()
symbol = self.AddEquity("SPY").Symbol
self.rvi = self.RVI(symbol, period)

# In OnData()
if self.rvi.IsReady:
    self.Plot("My Indicators", "signal", self.rvi.Signal.Current.Value)
    self.Plot("My Indicators", "relativevigorindex", self.rvi.Current.Value)
